            "title": "Whatinspired the creation of Toozi Sleepwear, and how does being a woman-owned,family business influence its design and craftsmanship?",
            "text": "<p><em>Toozi Sleepwear was born from a passion for crafting something truly special that<br/>elevates the sleepwear experience for everyone. We noticed that sleepwear often<br/>lacked purpose, so utilizing my experience in the fashion industry, I aimed to<br/>change that by designing sleepwear that allows individuals to sleep beautifully<br/>and look beautiful, just as they would when dressing for any other occasion.<br/>Our pieces are created with the intention of making you feel fabulous, even<br/>while you sleep, and we use premium bamboo fabrics to enhance that experience.</em></p><p><em> </em></p><p><em>As a<br/>woman-owned and family-run brand, we bring a unique perspective to our design<br/>and operations. We prioritize both comfort and style, ensuring our sleepwear<br/>complements the diverse lifestyles of our customers. By fostering close<br/>relationships with our team and customers, we create a sense of community and<br/>trust that larger brands often overlook. This intimate connection drives us to<br/>operate Toozi Sleepwear with integrity and passion, always committed to<br/>delivering quality and satisfaction.</em></p>"
