            "text": "<p><em>At Toozi, our sleepwear is crafted with love and care, reflecting the personal<br/>touch that defines our brand. I have had the privilege of visiting our talented<br/>team at StyleWorks, where our pieces are handmade. We are all directly involved<br/>in every step of the production process, from design to finishing touches,<br/>adding an intimate and thoughtful element to our creations.</em></p><p><em>We prioritize premium-quality fabrics that not only look luxurious but also<br/>enhance your comfort. One standout fabric is bamboo, known for its incredible<br/>softness, moisture-wicking properties, and natural hypoallergenic qualities.<br/>Choosing bamboo means you can sleep peacefully, knowing you're wrapped in both<br/>comfort and sustainability, making it the perfect choice for your nighttime<br/>routine.</em></p>"
